title: ISwPEClassFactory.SetPartnerKey
description: Sets the license key which SOLIDWORKS uses to verify SOLIDWORKS Partner entitlement.
signature:
System.Int32 SetPartnerKey( 
   System.String
StrPartnerEntitlement
,
   out System.Object
TokenObject
)

parameters.name: TokenObject
parameters.description: ISwPEToken ( for future use only - see Remarks )

returns: Return code as defined by swPartnerEntitlementStatus_e
remarks:
When this method is called, SOLIDWORKS compares the registry against these values in the license key specified in StrPartnerEntitlement:
SOLIDWORKS Partner entitlement
SOLIDWORKS version
Add-in name
Add-in GUID
Expiration date
See
SOLIDWORKS Partner Program
.
TokenObject is for future use only.
